           SPELL=qalculate
         VERSION=5.10.0
     SOURCE_HASH=sha512:ef4700e2bd946be11e10efad980e3cb0d02c058f13a5f7f62a8ccf3bd4bbc39035372152311174b808b4bb5ba3807152640121fd991c2b681370490e795f7139
          SOURCE=libqalculate-$VERSION.tar.gz
SOURCE_DIRECTORY=$BUILD_DIRECTORY/libqalculate-$VERSION
   SOURCE_URL[0]=https://github.com/Qalculate/libqalculate/releases/download/v${VERSION}/${SOURCE}
        WEB_SITE=https://qalculate.github.io
         ENTERED=20050208
      LICENSE[0]=GPL
        KEYWORDS="calculator science"
           SHORT="An advanced scientific calculator and simple CAS (Text
	   interface)"
cat << EOF
Qalculate! is a multi-purpose desktop calculator for GNU/Linux. 
It is small and simple to use but with much power and versatility underneath.
Features include customizable functions, units, arbitrary precision, plotting,
and a user-friendly interface.

This spell installs the qalculate library and a text interface. See the
qalculate-gtk and qalculate-kde spells for the gui versions.
EOF
